# Acme Operations

- **Frontend**: React + TypeScript (Vite)
- **Backend**: Django + Django REST Framework (DRF)

## Architecture principles

- Prefer clean, readable, maintainable code over clever abstractions
- Keep modules small and single-purpose
- UI: clean, modern, minimalistic — no visual clutter
- Never put business logic in views/components; use services (backend) and hooks/services (frontend)
